	<p>Good day all.<br />
<br />
I plan on making 34 in the next few days and was wondering how best to keep my new best friend happy.<br />
<br />
Aside from buffs and quickness what else should I do for him ?<br />
<br />
Is it worth spending a few PP on weapons or armor and handing them over ?<br />
<br />
I will have a 54 cleric around to buff us now and again.<br />
<br />
I think I have the combat strategies fairly well sussed out but any tips in this regard would also be happily accepted.<br />
<br />
Thanks - Lantril Lv 32 Iksar Shaman - Bristlebane</p>
	
	
	
