	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>Just keep the weapons that drop normally.  Velium weapons are great, but rusty daggers will work.  Kill skellies when you see them.<br />
<br />
I have never given my pet armor, except the summoned stuff.  I don't even AC buff him.  I do give him HP.  STA and AGI are a waste and DEX is, too, unless you have given him a proccing weapon.  STR has been debated, I used to give him clicky Jaundiced Bone Vambraces STR since it was free, now STR comes with Focus.</p>
	
	
	
