	<p>I focus my pet , for HP alone its worth it. Dpending on how tough the fights are ill  AC/AGI buff , i dont knoe if they do nything apart , cause i cast them bolth at the same time. But it does seem to help him last longer. Regen him too if you can , if its too much mana dont sweat it. The really big part is giving him procing weapons. Farm up gnoll hide lariats or farm up velium weapons , they will mage a huge difference untill you can proc mage summoned weapons. I fund that if you  just go to GD or split paw and offer buffs/pp for the weapons you can get them free or at very lil cost.</p>
	
	
	
